data.description: This magnificent two-story residence boasts five bedrooms and three bathrooms. On the upper floor, you'll find three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a welcoming eat-in kitchen, and a cozy family room. Downstairs, the lower level comprises two bedrooms, a well-appointed bathroom with a laundry area, a spacious living room, and a one-car garage. The driveway offers ample parking space for up to eight vehicles. A balcony graces the upper level, while a patio adorns the lower level. The backyard is securely enclosed for privacy, and a newly constructed 10x20 shed provides additional storage space. Harness the benefits of a solar power system, not only reducing your electricity bills but also contributing to environmental conservation. This home is meticulously designed to offer both comfort and convenience.
